        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Meanwhile, Trump’s Securities and Exchange Commission recently passed a new initiative making it harder for shareholders to ever introduce such resolutions, which are designed to let shareholders broadly shape policy at the corporations they own stock in.",
