            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "“In 2019, Amazon fulfillment centers recorded 14,000 serious injuries -- those requiring days off or job restrictions,” the outlet wrote. “The overall rate of 7.7 serious injuries per 100 employees was 33% higher than in 2016 and nearly double the most recent industry standard.”",
